<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />I will listen to what Yahweh God says,</para>

<para style="q1">for he will make peace with his people, his faithful followers.</para>

<para style="q1">Yet they must not turn again to foolish ways.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Surely his salvation is near to those who fear him;</para>

<para style="q1">then glory will remain in our land.</para>
